title: [Boil and Toil]
description: Crates, boxes and barrels are stacked and piles in the small backroom.  A worktable has been crafted with some boxes and planks of wood.  Several alchemist tools are set up on its surface.  They are surrounded by various bottles and packets and flasks filled with ingredients.
